<br />\n成功login到gmail就到改 appleid pw<br />\n<br />\n改appleid 冇得Login ipad/iphone下<br />\n唔一定可以<br />\n<br />\n因為而家就算收咗sms<br />\n佢都會要求你入2個安全問題<br />\n如果冇<br />\n<br />\n你就有可能要等外國apple批<br />\n就算你有死亡證，都唔一定批<br />\n<br />\n我fd就係冇盒冇單，香港ifc 冇嘢做到，而家等死亡證"},{"pid":"6f443fab33de8738592e2ae0fdfd80b5b35dc7b5","tid":2101321,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"冇朋友咪冇呢個煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3555de6a52a9ea92b4c68fc63d3111cf322b5b3f","tid":2101321,"uid":191410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"202c2228f724f4843b155f4c7a5aa5ac06b1be3a","tid":2101321,"uid":168389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T19:09:05.000Z","msg":"我香咗都唔知有無fd幫我搞後事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"依家真正嘅好朋友標準係幫你收屍"},{"pid":"51d2488870527234a629bdecbf2b11a08707da02","tid":2101321,"uid":191410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3555de6a52a9ea92b4c68fc63d3111cf322b5b3f","tid":2101321,"uid":191410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"202c2228f724f4843b155f4c7a5aa5ac06b1be3a","tid":2101321,"uid":168389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T19:09:05.000Z","msg":"我香咗都唔知有無fd幫我搞後事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"依家真正嘅好朋友標準係幫你收屍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"有你咁嘅好朋友佢真係好幸福， 真係唔想知可能畀咗一個課題我哋要珍惜眼前人，有咩就做咗先， 因為唔知第時有冇機會再同佢一齊做"},{"pid":"26f1466aa22d9c02860ec86182605d37d2747143","tid":2101321,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51d2488870527234a629bdecbf2b11a08707da02","tid":2101321,"uid":191410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3555de6a52a9ea92b4c68fc63d3111cf322b5b3f","tid":2101321,"uid":191410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"202c2228f724f4843b155f4c7a5aa5a